				<td colspan="2"><span>No you cant.
<br />

<br />
This songs works like regular Shadowstep does.
<br />

<br />
Teleports you (and the group members) to a random location and random distance away, within X feet (not sure how far) and within Line of Sight.
<br />

<br />
Cant stay inside a room, IE Shadowhaven Bank, and teleport outside (unless the door is open)
<br />

<br />
If it did port you inside locked doors, well... No more Rogue for Seb crypt, no more rogue for Chardok Royals chambers, no more rogue for CoM upper area...
<br />

<br />
Things would be a wee bit too easy (and unfair to rogues)</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
