				<td colspan="2"><span>Apparently a little-known fact, but any shadowstep will also *ALWAYS* be to a location at or below the same Z axis height it started at WITHOUT going through any area &quot;higher&quot; than the starting spot.  Very useful factoid for one particular PoFire fight, and for clever PVPers... 
<br />

<br />
i.e. in a limiting case, you can't shadowstep out of a depression, ever.
<br />

<br />
RdT. (and now TdB, Tello da Bard)</span></td>
